PM . Follow . Favorite
Joined 01-20-02, id: 157179, Profile Updated: 04-04-19
Author has written 400 stories for Transformers/Beast Wars, Hey Arnold, Teen Titans, Power Rangers, Centurions, Spider-Man, MASK, Ninja Turtles, Simpsons, Sherlock, Wizards vs. Aliens, Space Ghost, Doctor Who, Wrestling, Jackie Chan Adventures, Thunderbirds, Danger Mouse, Bob's Burgers, Batman Beyond, Terrahawks, Black Mirror, British Comedy, Pokémon, Scooby Doo, Sliders, Avengers, Outer Limits, Orville, Knight Rider, Torchwood, Johnny Bravo, Superman, Demon Headmaster, Star Wars, and Terminator.

Hello folks, my name's Zarius. I'm a fan of many things, but mostly of the little things. The shows, comics, and characters we take for granted in this day and age. From former t.v giants to underdog comic book runs, to the shows very few have heard of, I aim to give as many of them as loud a voice as possible, and in doing so maybe inspire more to start contributing their own voice.

I finally joined Archive of Our Own, user name is the same: Zarius. Come follow me there too.

Recently I've been going in and revising some of my older fanfics due to finding grammatical or structural errors in them, so if you see a fanfic and it reads differently from when you last glanced at it, it's usually a result of that.
